# U-Boot environment configuration for GlassOS.
# Points libubootenv (and therefore RAUC) at the glassos-bootstate raw partition.
# The environment block starts at offset 0 and is 16 KiB long.
#
# Device                              Offset   Env size   Flash sector size
/dev/disk/by-partlabel/glassos-bootstate  0x0000   0x4000

